---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy" 
  description="Privacy Policy for Dr. Sanjay Swamy's Clinic."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content">
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We strictly collect only the information necessary for medical treatment and appointment scheduling. This includes your name, contact details, and the child's medical history.</p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>Your data is used solely for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Scheduling appointments</li>
        <li>Maintaining medical records</li>
        <li>Communicating test results and health updates</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement strict security measures to protect your personal health information. We do not sell or share your data with third parties unless required by law or for medical referral purposes (with your consent).</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about our privacy practices, please contact us at privacy@drsanjayswamy.com.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header { background-color: var(--color-background); padding: 3rem 0; text-align: center; }
  .content { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  h2 { margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary-dark); }
  ul { margin-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
</style>
